rogress spinner, Rich success output for both providers, `_handle_error` integration |\n| **PublishRuntime** | `.../cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | 216 | **Implemented** -- Full class with `publish()`, `_prepare_image_for_publishing()`, `_prepare_local_image()`, `_prepare_cloud_image()`, `_publish_cr_to_k8s()`, `_publish_k8s()`, `_update_publish_metadata()` |\n| **DockerService** | `.../cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | 131 | **Implemented** -- `push_image()`, `_docker_login_sdk()`, `_tag_image_sdk()`, `check_docker_available()`, `build_image()` |\n| **AgentCubeProvider** | `.../cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | 135 | **Implemented** -- `deploy_agent_runtime()`, `get_agent_runtime()`, `_sanitize_name()`, CRD group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` |\n| **KubernetesProvider** | `.../cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` | 205 | **Implemented** -- `deploy_agent()`, `wait_for_deployment_ready()`, `delete_agent()`, Deployment + NodePort Service creation |\n| **MetadataService** | `.../cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | 130 | **Implemented** -- `AgentMetadata` Pydantic model, `load_metadata()`, `save_metadata()`, `update_metadata()` |\n| **Package __init__.py** | `.../cmd/cli/agentcube/__init__.py` | 12 | **Implemented** -- Exports `app`, `PackRuntime`, `BuildRuntime`, `PublishRuntime` |\n| **Runtime __init__.py** | `.../cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | 8 | **Implemented** -- Re-exports `PackRuntime`, `BuildRuntime`, `PublishRuntime`, `MetadataOptions` |\n\n---\n\n### 3. Test Files -- What Exists\n\n| Test File | Path | Status |\n|-----------|------|--------|\n| **PublishRuntime tests** | `.../cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py` | **Present** (346 lines, ~20 test classes) |\n| **DockerService tests** | `.../cmd/cli/tests/services/test_docker_service.py` | **Present** (226 lines) |\n| **AgentCubeProvider tests** | `.../cmd/cli/tests/services/test_agentcube_provider.py` | **Present** (142 lines) |\n| **KubernetesProvider tests** | `.../cmd/cli/tests/services/test_k8s_provider.py` | **Present** (141 lines) |\n\n---\n\n### 4. What Is MISSING or INCOMPLETE\n\n#### Missing Test Files (per tasks.md):\n| Missing File | Tasks Reference | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `tests/cli/test_publish_command.py` | T9.6-T9.17 | CLI-level publish command tests (12 test cases) |\n| `tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime_metadata.py` | T8.2-T8.7, T6.3, T7.3 | Metadata update tests for both providers |\n| `tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime_image.py` | T5.4-T5.15 | Image preparation flow tests (12 test cases) |\n| `tests/integration/test_publish_e2e.py` | T10.1-T10.7 | End-to-end integration tests (7 test cases) |\n\n#### Missing Commands (per cli-toolkit spec, but NOT part of AR-022 scope):\n| Missing Item | Notes |\n|---|---|\n| `invoke` command in `main.py` | Belongs to AR-023, not AR-022 |\n| `status` command in `main.py` | Belongs to AR-023, not AR-022 |\n| `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | Belongs to AR-023 |\n| `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | Belongs to AR-023 |\n\n#### Code Gaps/Bugs Identified by Verification (ST-6):\n\n| Bug | File | Root Cause |\n|---|---|---|\n| `_update_publish_metadata` does not save `version`, `description`, `region` | `publish_runtime.py` line 206-216 | Only saves `agent_id`, `agent_endpoint`, `k8s_deployment` -- the version/description/region overrides are set on the in-memory metadata object but `_update_publish_metadata` does not include them in the updates dict |\n| Docker unavailable check fires before provider validation | `publish_runtime.py` line 54 | `_prepare_image_for_publishing` (which checks Docker) is called before the unknown provider check in `_publish_cr_to_k8s`/`_publish_k8s` routing, so an unknown provider with local build mode triggers Docker check first |\n| Pydantic error message mismatch | `metadata_service.py` | Pydantic raises `\"Unsupported build_mode: ...\"` but test expects `\"Unsupported build mode\"` (underscore vs space) |\n| `model_copy(update=...)` does not trigger validation | `metadata_service.py` line 108 | Pydantic's `model_copy(update=...)` bypasses validators, so invalid language values pass through |\n| YAML format test failure | `metadata_service.py` line 93 | `model_dump(exclude_none=True)` excludes empty-string fields, producing different YAML than expected |\n\n---\n\n### 5. Verification Results (ST-6 Final Report)\n\n**Overall: 160 passed, 7 failed, 1 skipped** (out of 168 tests)\n\nThe 7 failures are:\n1. `test_invalid_language_raises` -- `_apply_option_overrides` doesn't trigger Pydantic validation\n2. `test_raises_value_error_for_unknown_provider` -- Docker check fires before provider validation\n3. `test_raises_value_error_for_unknown_build_mode` -- Pydantic error message mismatch\n4. `test_version_is_updated_in_metadata` -- `_update_publish_metadata` doesn't save version\n5. `test_description_is_updated_in_metadata` -- Same issue\n6. `test_region_is_updated_in_metadata` -- Same issue\n7. `test_yaml_format` -- `exclude_none=True` excludes empty-string fields\n\n---\n\n### 6. Git History\n\nNo publish-specific commits were found in the git log. The git history contains only benchmark infrastructure commits (report generation, cost corrections, etc.), not feature development commits. This is expected -- the workspace was created by an AI coding agent during the benchmark run, not via incremental git commits.\n\n---\n\n### 7. TODO Comments\n\n**No TODO/FIXME/HACK/XXX comments** were found in any Python source files under `cmd/cli/`. The codebase appears clean of deferred items in the implementation files.\n\n---\n\n### 8. Summary Assessment\n\n**AR-022 is substantially implemented but has 7 test failures and 4 missing test files.**\n\n| Dimension | Status |\n|---|---|\n| Proposal | Complete |\n| Delta Spec | Complete |\n| Design | Complete |\n| Tasks | Complete |\n| CLI command entry point | Implemented |\n| PublishRuntime class | Implemented |\n| DockerService (push_image, login, tag) | Implemented |\n| AgentCubeProvider (CR deployment) | Implemented |\n| KubernetesProvider (Deployment + Service) | Implemented |\n| MetadataService (load/save/update) | Implemented |\n| PublishRuntime unit tests | Present but has bugs |\n| DockerService tests | Present |\n| AgentCubeProvider tests | Present |\n| KubernetesProvider tests | Present |\n| CLI command tests | **MISSING** |\n| Image preparation tests | **MISSING** |\n| Metadata update tests | **MISSING** |\n| E2E integration tests | **MISSING** |\n| Code quality (ruff, mypy) | Not yet verified |\n| Test coverage >= 80% | Not yet verified |\n\nThe core publish functionality (both agentcube and k8s providers, image preparation, CLI command) is fully coded. The remaining work consists of:\n1. Fixing the 7 failing tests (mostly in `_update_publish_metadata` and error ordering)\n2. Writing the 4 missing test files\n3. Running code quality gates (ruff, mypy, coverage)\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_286c6dc94ffeALxWQ7I7AwqMZ2","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube CLI publish","time":{"start":1775855280999,"end":1775855428991}}}}
